quota_attainment.query: a = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; a = filter a by {{column(dropdown_id_hidden.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field")}}; a = filter a by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; a = filter a by date('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Year', 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Month', 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current_period").asObject()}}]; b = load "${App.Datasets.quota.Alias}"; b = filter b by {{column(dropdown_id_hidden.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("User.UniqueUserName")}}; b = filter b by date('StartDate_Year', 'StartDate_Month', 'StartDate_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asObject()}}]; c = group a by all full, b by all; c = foreach c generate (case when sum(a['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) / sum(b['QuotaAmount']) > 0 then round(sum(a['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) / sum(b['QuotaAmount']), 2) else 0 end) as 'sum_quota_attainment';

query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_pipelinetrending_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter q by {{column(dropdown_id_hidden.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("Opportunity.Owner.UniqueUserName")}}; q = filter q by 'Stage.IsClosed' == "false"; this_year = filter q by date('RPLCM_PipelineTrending_CloseDate_Field_Year', 'RPLCM_PipelineTrending_CloseDate_Field_Month', 'RPLCM_PipelineTrending_CloseDate_Field_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asObject()}}]; last_year = filter q by date('RPLCM_PipelineTrending_CloseDate_Field_Year', 'RPLCM_PipelineTrending_CloseDate_Field_Month', 'RPLCM_PipelineTrending_CloseDate_Field_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "prior").asObject()}}]; last_year = filter last_year by date('ValidFromDate_Year', 'ValidFromDate_Month', 'ValidFromDate_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "validfrom").asString()}}]; last_year = filter last_year by date('ValidToDate_Year', 'ValidToDate_Month', 'ValidToDate_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "validto").asString()}}]; result = group this_year by all full, last_year by all; result = foreach result generate coalesce((sum(this_year['Amount']) - sum(last_year['Amount']))/sum(last_year['Amount']),0) as 'sum_percent', sum(last_year['Amount']) as 'last_year'; result = foreach result generate 'sum_percent','last_year', (case when 'sum_percent' > 0 then "#067D1E" when 'sum_percent' < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#7D98B3" end) as 'color';

kpi_quota.query: b = load "${App.Datasets.quota.Alias}"; b = filter b by {{column(dropdown_id_hidden.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("User.UniqueUserName")}}; b = group b by all; b = filter b by date('StartDate_Year', 'StartDate_Month', 'StartDate_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asObject()}}]; b = foreach b generate sum('QuotaAmount') as 'sum_quota_attainment', sum('QuotaAmount')*.9 as 'ninety_percent', sum('QuotaAmount')*.7 as 'seventy_percent', sum('QuotaAmount')*.5 as 'fifty_percent';

query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.activity.Alias}"; q = filter q by {{column(dropdown_id_hidden.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("Owner.UniqueUserName")}}; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "false"; this_year = filter q by date('ActivityDate_Year', 'ActivityDate_Month', 'ActivityDate_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asObject()}}]; last_year = filter q by date('ActivityDate_Year', 'ActivityDate_Month', 'ActivityDate_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "prior").asObject()}}]; this_year = foreach this_year generate count() as 'completed_activities'; last_year = foreach last_year generate count() as 'completed_activities'; result = group this_year by all full, last_year by all; result = foreach result generate coalesce((sum(this_year['completed_activities']) - sum(last_year['completed_activities']))/sum(last_year['completed_activities']),0) as 'sum_percent', sum(last_year['completed_activities']) as 'last_year'; result = foreach result generate 'sum_percent','last_year', (case when 'sum_percent' > 0 then "#067D1E" when 'sum_percent' < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#7D98B3" end) as 'color';

q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter q by {{column(dropdown_id_hidden.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field")}}; q = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true";this_year = filter q by date('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Year', 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Month', 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current_period").asObject()}}]; last_year = filter q by date('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Year', 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Month', 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_Day') in [{{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "prior_period").asObject()}}]; this_year = foreach this_year generate sum('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field') as 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field';last_year = foreach last_year generate sum('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field') as 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field';result = group this_year by all full, last_year by all; result = foreach result generate coalesce((sum(this_year['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) - sum(last_year['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']))/sum(last_year['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_percent', sum(last_year['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) as 'last_year'; result = foreach result generate 'sum_percent','last_year', (case when 'sum_percent' > 0 then "#067D1E" when 'sum_percent' < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#7D98B3" end) as 'color';
